Cell["\<\
The most dangerous case is that the check operator commutes with all of the \
generators but does not belong to the stabilizer. To check if there is such \
case, we examine the check operators that commute with all of the generators.\
\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->765787684,ExpressionUUID->"d81851c0-68bc-4e34-845a-6f8fc65584fd"],

