 CellID->920146492,ExpressionUUID->"d2808e41-f16c-4d3e-92b6-3933edcd4610"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
This shows that such check operators actually belong to the stabilizer. The \
considered errors are thus correctable by the code.\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->803508420,ExpressionUUID->"cfabc333-23a0-41a3-8f47-c2e997b421ef"],

