       OverscriptBox["0", "_"]}]},
    "Ket"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "14bef535-cb79-48b9-944a-f3c6049a0f33"],
 " in five physical qubits."
}], "TechNoteMathCaption",
