Cell["\<\
Prepare the five-qubit system in a linear superposition of all computational \
basis states. This state is useful because it is likely to have support in \
every eigenspace of the observables that we are going to measure below. \
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->508922988,ExpressionUUID->"b5462712-f63a-468a-8256-438c6bd77b9e"],

